        <updateDate>2018-02-21T22:15:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Justice Safety Valve Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to authorize a court to impose a sentence below the mandatory minimum if it determines, after considering certain factors, that the mandatory minimum sentence is greater than necessary.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
